		RTL8181 Application Development Kit- v1.5
		-----------------------------------------

Package List
============
  1. rtl8181-toolchain-1.1.tar.gz - containing the toolchain to build Linux
     kernel and application for RTL8181.
  2. rtl8181-ASP-1.5.tar.gz - Application Source Package v1.5, containing
     Linux kernel object modules and the all application soruces and script 
     files adopted in RTL8181 turnkey solution.


Environment
===========
  RedHat 7.3 is recommended.


Install ToolChain
=================
  1. Copy 'rtl8181-toolchain-1.1.tar.gz' to a file directory on a Linux PC.
  2. Type 'tar xfzv rtl8181-toolchain-1.1.tar.gz' to extract the package.
  3. Read file 'rtl8181-toolchain-1.1\INSTALL' and follow the instruction
     to install the toolchain.


Install and Build Linux System
==============================
  1. Copy 'rtl8181-ASP-1.5.tar.gz' to a file directory on a Linux PC.
  2. Type 'tar xfzv rtl8181-ASP-1.5.tar.gz' to extract the package.
  3. Read 'README' and 'INSTALL' files in 'rtl8181-ASP-1.5' directory,
     and follow the instruction to install and build the package.

